item.title: Version 25
item.description: Value Set Version Description:Event code list for 2018.Changes from 2017: Added Hepatitis C, perinatal infection, Paratyphoid fever (caused by Salmonella serotypes Paratyphi A, Paratyphi B [tartrate negative], and Paratyphi C), Salmonellosis, (excluding paratyphoid fever and typhoid fever), and Syphilis, unknown duration or late to the list.Renamed Syphilis, early latent to Syphilis, early non-primary, non-secondary and Perinatal Hepatitis B virus infection to Hepatitis B, perinatal infection.Removed Salmonellosis, Syphilis, late latent, Syphilis, late with clinical manifestations (including late benign syphilis and cardiovascular syphilis) from the list.

item.title: Version 23
item.description: Value Set Version Description:Event code list for 2017 Changes from 2016:The name for Streptococcus pneumoniae, invasive disease (IPD) (all ages) was revised to Invasive pneumococcal disease (11723)Removed Zika virus disease, non-congenital infection (11726)Removed Zika virus, congenital infection (11736)Added three conditions that are under standardized surveillance Acanthamoeba disease (excluding keratitis) (50225)Balamuthia mandrillaris disease (50226)Naegleria fowleri causing Primary Amebic Meningoencephalitis (50227)

item.title: Version 22
